value.string: Wailea Point 2301 is a single-level ground floor unit with excellent ocean views towards the West Maui mountains. You will enjoy privacy with water views from the inside living area, the kitchen and from the lanai. The sunrise and moonrise vistas towards the top of famous Haleakala mountain, are a stunning bonus. There are NO steps from the one-car garage all the way through the end of the uncovered lanai. Wailea Point 2301 is centrally located in the upper tier of the complex and in close proximity to the main pool area. The elegant interior remodel includes hard wood floors throughout the unit, an open kitchen with light marble counters, an oversized sink and newer stainless steel appliances. Most of the lights are low-voltage recessed ceiling lights that operate with dimmers to set the right mood. With few exclusions, this offering is fully furnished. Comparing Wailea Point 2301 to competing Wailea Condos listed for sale, this is an exceptional value.

The very best OCEAN ViIEW value in all of Wailea Beach Villas. A terrific opportunity to own this large spacious 2 bedroom 2 bath with den condominium in Wailea's finest oceanfront complex. All of the benefits of a world class property offering guard gated entry, concierge services, front desk management - all on beautiful tropical grounds complete with waterfalls and flowing water features. Located adjacent to the sandy Wailea Beach, and in immediate proximity to the Four Seasons and the Grand Wailea hotels, fine dining, beach activities and the Shops at Wailea make this the complete resort destination. The unit is currently in the rental program and offers a seasoned clientele. Make an appointment to view Wailea Beach Villas and see why it was voted Hawaii's #1 resort in 2014

Largest Penthouse in Wailea Beach Villas; the award winning BEACHFRONT condominium complex. WBV was voted the #1 resort property in Hawaii by Conde Nast Traveller and #11 in the entire U.S. This exclusive community offers luxurious on-site amenities and is walking distance to Wailea's Five-Star hotels, premier shops, fine restaurants and world-class spas. PH 208 has been home-away-from-home for the owners; the three bedroom condo is in impeccable condition, never rented by the current owners and is move-in ready. Contemporary design with top of the line finishes, granite counter tops, central air conditioning and outdoor barbeque grill. Gated entry with guard, 24/7 security, two swimming pools and beach services on Wailea Beach, including towels and cabanas. Two lounges for private events, a game room with kitchen, a state-of-the-art fitness center, fully accessorized business center and a conference room are available to owners and guests.

A significant step above! This pristine fourth-floor 2/bedroom, 2/bath Penthouse Unit (with den/office) commands sweeping views of Pacific Ocean blue, outer islands, Wailea beach, plus the southern slope of magnificent Haleakala descending to Makena. This is a rare offering. Beach Villa 411has never been rented, only occasionally occupied by owners, and meticulously maintained. Conde Nast readers proclaimed Wailea Beach Villas #1Resort in Hawaii in 2014. There are reasons aplenty. The resort features two pools, state-of-the art fitness center, 24-hour gated security, entertainment lounges, game room, business center and conference room, concierge services- and direct access to Wailea Beach. The Villas owners have a private gateway to The Shops at Wailea where shopping and dining options abound. Interior appointments are exceptional: Gourmet kitchen designed and built by Studio Becker, Sub Zero refrigerator, Gaggano cooktop; Travertine flooring, granite/marble counter tops and limestone/marble baths. The list of amenities goes on,but the time is now! Fully furnished, unoccupied and very easy to show with short notice.

Wailea Point is situated on over 26 spectacular ocean front acres. Unit 801 offers nice ocean views, and is conveniently located between the owner's gym, the family pool, and the quiet pool area close to the beach. Unit 801 is the largest standard floor plan at Wailea Point. Consisting of 3 bedrooms, 4 bedrooms, and an excellent location... this unit is constructed with integrity that stands the test of time. Other amenities include lighted tennis courts, and an entertainment pavilion with barbecues. Golf carts allowed.

Wailea Point is proudly positioned upon 28 'Premier Oceanfront' Acres in The World Class Wailea Resort, next door to The Four Seasons. It offers guard gated & 24 hour roving security. Location! Location! Location! Wailea Point #2404 is considered the 'Premier Location' within this low density, treasured, tropical paradise. Unobstructed 'Panoramic Views' encompass Wailea Beach, the entire S. Maui Coastline, the West Maui Mountains, the Islands of Lanai & Kahoolawe, Iconic Molokini Crater & Pu'u Hoolai in Makena. This immaculately maintained 3 bedroom, 4 bath, two story unit 'lives large' encompassing 2 private ocean view lanais totaling 574 s.f. Upon entering you are transfixed upon the perfectly framed view of the West Maui Mountains. The vaulted clear cedar ceilings & perimeter soffits with recessed copper-toned art lighting, marble entry area & book-matched Koa doors add a feeling of warmth & elegance. Numerous skylights & clear-story windows fill the interior with tropical light. The upstairs spacious Master Suite offers 'his & her' private bathrooms, lofted ceilings & 'crows nest' views from the private lanai. A main level second master bedroom with en-suite bathroom offers two private vanity areas. There is also a lovely guest suite, powder room & laundry area. The wrap-around main level lanai offers alfresco dining, a BBQ, & electric privacy / sunshades. A glass on glass corner kitchen window affords inspiring views & culinary creativity. Second to none on Maui are the two exclusive on-site recreation areas, one is family oriented & includes a lap pool & state of the art gym, while the other is the 'quiet' pool area. Experience the Best Maui has to offer as you drive your golf cart or stroll through these 28 pastoral acres with direct access to two pristine beaches, the adjacent oceanfront 'Wailea Walk', fine dining & shopping at The Shops of Wailea & the spas of Maui's finest resorts. World class golf is just across the street & tennis courts are onsite. ***Be sure to view the Virtual Aerial Tour.***
